NEW += '                    <div class="sec-title">State Evolution for Each Sub-Variant Group</div>\n'
NEW += '                    <div class="info-box" style="line-height:1.75">\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 1: Single Digit Constraint</strong><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Stage 1:</strong> dp[pos][tight] = count of valid completions<br>\n'
NEW += '                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0;font-size:.78rem"><code>Recurrence:\n'
NEW += '  limit = bound[pos] if tight else 9\n'
NEW += '  dp[pos][tight] = SUM_&#123;d=0..limit&#125; dp[pos+1][tight AND (d==limit)]\n'
NEW += '    (d rejected if violates property)\n'
NEW += 'Base: dp[n][tight] = 1  (n digits placed; one valid number)\n'
NEW += 'Preferred: TOP-DOWN with memo &mdash; tight=true branch differs per bound;\n'
NEW += '  tight=false is fully reusable across queries.</code></pre>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Stage 2:</strong> dp[pos][tight][prev] &mdash; adds previous digit; property(d, prev) checked per placement.<br><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Stage 3:</strong> dp[pos][tight][leading][digit_sum] &mdash; adds digit sum accumulator.<br>\n'
NEW += '                        next_leading = leading AND (d == 0); next_sum = sum + (0 if next_leading else d)<br>\n'
NEW += '                        Base: dp[n][tight][leading][sum] = 1 if sum satisfies property else 0<br><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 3: Modular Constraint (Number mod K)</strong><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Stage 2:</strong> dp[pos][tight][mod_val] &mdash; the partial NUMBER value mod K<br>\n'
NEW += '                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0;font-size:.78rem"><code>Recurrence:\n'
NEW += '  dp[pos][tight][mod] = SUM_&#123;d&#125; dp[pos+1][...][(mod*10 + d) % K]\n'
NEW += 'Base: dp[n][tight][mod] = 1 if mod==0 else 0\n'
NEW += '\n'
NEW += 'KEY DISTINCTION: tracks VALUE of the number mod K, not digit-sum mod K.\n'
NEW += 'Recurrence is (mod * 10 + d) % K &mdash; "shift left and add" in base 10.\n'
NEW += 'Optimisation (large K): meet-in-the-middle &mdash; split digits into halves,\n'
NEW += '  enumerate all (half_value, count) per half, join via hashmap.</code></pre>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 2: Bitmask of Used Digits</strong><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Stage 3:</strong> dp[pos][tight][leading][mask]<br>\n'
NEW += '                        next_leading = leading AND (d == 0); next_mask = mask if next_leading else (mask | (1 &lt;&lt; d))<br>\n'
NEW += '                        Base: dp[n][...][mask] = 1 if popcount(mask) &le; K else 0 (or mask == (1&lt;&lt;10)&minus;1 for pandigital)<br>\n'
NEW += '                        State size: 18 &times; 2 &times; 2 &times; 1024 &asymp; 74,000. Precompute popcount for all 1024 masks.<br><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 4: Sum DP (Tuple Return)</strong><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Stage 3:</strong> dp returns (count, total_value_sum)<br>\n'
NEW += '                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0;font-size:.78rem"><code>For each valid digit d:\n'
NEW += '  (sub_count, sub_sum) = dp[pos+1][...]\n'
NEW += '  contribution of d at pos = d * 10^remaining * sub_count\n'
NEW += '  total_count += sub_count\n'
NEW += '  total_sum   += sub_sum + d * 10^remaining * sub_count\n'
NEW += 'Base: dp[n][...] = (1, 0)   # one number, tail sum = 0\n'
NEW += 'Precompute pow10[0..18] to avoid recomputation.</code></pre>\n'
NEW += '                    </div>\n'
